caption: Establishment of Reserve Fund
created: 20260318120000000
modified: 20260318120000000
title: Policy3432(1)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Regional School District 8 Board of Education hereby establishes the Reserve Fund for Educational Expenditures (the "Account") pursuant to Section § 10-51d(2) of the Connecticut General Statutes, as amended, which Account shall be a non-lapsing account. Any funds from the prior account shall be transferred to the new Account and shall be used for the purposes described herein.